##OPTIONS
#-b -> always make (unconditionaly)
#-c -> directory
#-d -> debugging information
#--debug[=FLAGS] - a ->all b-basic v-more verbose i-implicit rules j-#details of commands invokation m-debug while ramking
#-e -> variables from environment files override make file
#-i ->ignore errors
#-I -> incluir directorios para procurar por outrous makes?
#-j[jobs] -> numero de Trabalhos a correr em simultaneo (default sem limite)
#-l[load] -> maximo de carga (nao comeca nova compilacao se o trabalho for maior)
#-n print the comands but do not execute them
#-o do not remage file if it is older than its dependencies
#-s -> silent (dont print comands)

